<BlogLayout
  title="What Does ATP Mean in Text? (At This Point vs Answer The Phone)"
  description="ATP in text means 'At This Point' in most contexts, or 'Answer The Phone' when someone is not picking up calls. See examples of both usages."
  canonical="/blog/what-does-atp-mean-in-text"
